  "chapter": {
    "number": 12,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Joyful Thanksgiving"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          "In that day you will say:",
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          {
            "text": "“O LORD, I will praise You.",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "Although You were angry with me,",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "Your anger has turned away,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "and You have comforted me.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Surely God is my salvation;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "I will trust and not be afraid.",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "For the LORD GOD is my strength and my song,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "and He also has become my salvation.”",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          "With joy you will draw water from the springs of salvation,"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          "and on that day you will say:",
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          {
            "text": "“Give praise to the LORD;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "proclaim His name!",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "Make His works known among the peoples;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "declare that His name is exalted.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sing to the LORD, for He has done glorious things.",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "Let this be known in all the earth.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cry out and sing, O citizen of Zion,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "for great among you is the Holy One of Israel.”",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
